title: Papa Gino's with John Hodgman, Jean Grae, and Jeff Tweedy
itunes:title: Papa Gino's with John Hodgman, Jean Grae, and Jeff Tweedy
description:
In Mitch's home state of Massachusetts, the 'boys are joined by John Hodgman (Vacationland, Judge John Hodgman), Jean Grae (Everything's Fine), and Jeff Tweedy (Wilco) to review a New England native chain, Papa Gino's.

Recorded live on June 29th in North Adams, Mass. as part of the Solid Sound Festival.

Want more Doughboys? Check out our Patreon!: https://patreon.com/doughboys
